<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_a9276574-bc8f-4f07-ab54-191fdff44181" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>C2P1</sptc><title id="_df8a9b06-6382-4fe5-8a93-12086ad5db0f">Disposal</title><archive-num>2019: CP2.1</archive-num><subclause id="_df85a179-ca98-4bc2-be0f-643234a5f6b0" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_108112b1-05fa-45cf-aa39-4646aebc5937">SubClause</title><num/><p>Sewage must be conveyed through a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1249_0.8.0.xml#_25307451-c7e1-4167-b4de-e5a1af26694c" id="_42819034-725b-47fd-90f7-6bc512713710" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage</xref> system to an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1193_0.6.0.xml#_9d2e065b-aa41-45f9-b2f5-4628d8fa28d0" id="_fa05f58d-3b12-4a4b-b327-e19434c74037" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">approved disposal system</xref> authorised by an authority having jurisdiction.</p></subclause><callout id="_e9755f61-fa5d-4ee9-96b7-3d8243f6bf6b"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>An <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1193_0.6.0.xml#_9d2e065b-aa41-45f9-b2f5-4628d8fa28d0" id="_439e22a2-eb30-4078-aa7b-6830c07046a0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">approved disposal system</xref> may be—</p><ol outputclass="numbered"><li id="_51d81fd0-1680-4a0f-91d6-4f4f27978f56">an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1383_4.5.0.xml#_2396187d-8435-4f01-9dfd-613970a74823" id="_735df502-6d62-45cc-9507-f5537c07c717" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">on-site wastewater management system</xref>; or</li><li id="_8fb0685a-97ab-48eb-bade-7fe0fbee2355">a connection to a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_ba422dbf-14a1-4c21-ba1b-2402d592b94d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator's</xref> sewerage system.</li></ol></callout></clause>